[[de:Production Designer]]

A '''textbook exchange''' is the selling or trading of [[textbook]]s used from a previous college [[semester]] to students needing that textbook for the current semester. It is primarily aimed to fight the rising cost of college books.<ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2005/09/04/business/yourmoney/04text.html?_r=1&scp=2&sq=textbook%20exchange&st=cse New York Times: Sometimes, It's Not the Tuition. It's the Textbooks]</ref> Exchanges may be made at the [[college bookstore]] or through a website.
